{
  "stem": "26576.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And a lot of people so went for it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And actually, it saved a lot of lives.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Because my mother would cook a big pot of beet root.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And there were a lot of lonely people, single people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And she would feed whoever was hungry, really.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my father got a job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And somehow life settled.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why did he intend to go to Merke?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was there a particular reason?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no, really.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, many-- this is the very interesting part that everything at that stage was done-- look we never, we didn't know what Merke is.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know what Kazakhstan is.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We could have-- you know Merke was a spot that somebody told him that there is that sugar factory.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he worked it out in his mind.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A lot of things were a matter of luck during the war, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A lot of our friends later on, afterward, that we met some went to [INAUDIBLE] and some went-- I met now, I met a lady that was five or six kilometers from close to Merke, but I've never knew her.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was also there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People went where they felt that maybe they'll be able to survive there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, a small thing will trigger it off.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like because there was a big-- that [INAUDIBLE] people we're thinking, well maybe we'll get a job there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Having a job, you've got already chance to survive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was the reason.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Also he told it's warm, it's a warmer climate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was warm, but it wasn't a good climate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was exactly like, like north of China.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The winters were bitterly cold, and the summers were very hot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the conditions that we were living were also terrible.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And a lot, a lot of people died from typhoid.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
